# Documentation Folder

This folder contains supporting documents that explain the design and usage of the reflection system.

## Files

* `write-up.md`
  Explains the design rationale, psychological foundations, and structure of the reflection tree.

* `reference-guide.txt`
  Provides a technical guide to understand the file formats, node types, and how to view the files.

## Purpose

This folder helps reviewers understand:

* The thinking behind the design
* How the system works
* How to navigate and interpret the files
